== Overview ==
Using an EM induction wave, the Syphon is capable of causing significant energy loss to an enemy. Shields or armor are ineffective at stopping the drain.

== Where to Acquire ==
The EM Syphon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
